Flexible commercial loans









 

commercial real estate loans


ReadyCap's commercial loans provide an investment financing solution to borrowers who need flexibility to capitalize on current commercial real estate market opportunities. We created a small-balance financing program to help borrowers close on their investment projects. ReadyCap lends in major markets nationwide for both commercial property acquisition and refinance.
Available in major markets nationwide, our commercial investment loans from $750,000 to $10,000,000 offer financing for office, retail, industrial, self-storage, mixed use and single tenants and mixed-use commercial real estate. Designed specifically to exceed the expectations of the experienced borrower, the advantages of ReadyCap’s investment financing are:





Leverage up to 75% of appraised value
Purchase, refinance or cash-out
Prepay flexibility
Interest-only, 15, 20, 25 & 30
Min 1.25x (UW NOI)
Quick closings

    ReadyCap's commercial real estate loans support a wide array of transaction scenarios:


Non-recourse available
Loan amounts too small for CMBS
Properties without historic financials considered
Foreign national borrower
Up to 10-year fixed terms
15-, 20-, 25- or 30-year amortization options
Properties that do not meet conventional underwriting criteria 
Lower occupancy with strong cash flow

We offer a common-sense underwriting approach that takes into consideration all factors of the deal. We pride ourselves on delivering five-star, concierge-like service, with innovative financing solutions. Download our Commercial Loan Product Sheet, or give us a call today: 888-354-0822.




















